  D4LM's License protects the developer D4LM's and his accosiates with
two steps: (1) assert copyright on the software, and (2) offer you 
this License which gives you legal permission to copy, distribute and/or
modify the software as long as you meet D4LM's terms.

  D4LM's License allows those wanting to make a modified version to let 
public access without releasing the source code as long the new 
